nce.  All these options require putting skill pint into an additional style line and giving up shield defence.  The comparison below is based on my understanding of the game, and as such may be wrong.  If you now any of this is wrong please correct me.<br>
<br>
With a Polearm there is a 40% increase in damage. So this lvl 50 char will average 1.4*N unstyled dps.<br>
<br>
LA always swings twice but damage per hit is a percentage of a normal hit (60 + lvl/2) percent. So with a modified LA skill of 50 the average unstyled dps would be 2 * 0.85 = 1.7*N dps.<br>
<br>
With DW the percentage chance to swing is (25 + lvl/4 + DW/2).  So at lvl 50 with a modified DW of 50 the chance to swing twice is 62.5%.  So average unstyled damage is 1.625*N dps.<br>
<br>
Not too bad for DW.  A bit less than LA but more than polearm.  But the real naffness of DW is when you look at styled damage.<br>
<br>
For all these comparisons lets take a mythical style with a growth rate that gives a 1.8 multiplier.<br>
<br>
Normal single weapon will do 1.8*N dps, and lets call this M dps.<br>
<br>
Polearm will do 1.4 * 1.8 = 2.52*N dps (1.4*M)<br>
<br>
LA will do 1.7 * 1.8 = 3.06*N dps (1.7*M)<br>
<br>
DW will do 1.8 + .625 = 2.425*N dps (1.35*M) (only main hand gets style bonus)<br>
<br>
But it gets worse because the DW growth rates are so bad. The pole arm and LA styles will give bigger multipliers.<br>
<br>
The poor old DW is screwed.  At the very least the style bonus needs to be applied to both swings for DW.  On a personal note I would rather swing both hands every round at the average speed and hit for less with each, just like the LA mechanics, rather than have a percentage chance to hit at full damage.  More predictable, more hits, more procs, bring down PBT more.<br>
<br>
DW has to be improved! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fingoniel>Fingoniel</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://forums.barrysworld.com/avatar.php?userid=16042&dateline=1026917502" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Determined Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 357<br> <font color=#000000>(7/7/03 4:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=278.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Why merc damage sucks</span><hr size=1> only the mainhand for LA gets the style bonus (it's calculated before the left axe reduction too)<br>
